Use 24-Hour MVP Mode.

Goal:
Build the smallest production-deployable version that proves the core user journey.

Rules:
- No unnecessary abstractions.
- No new dependency unless critical.
- No custom design system unless already present.
- Use existing Supabase client pattern.
- Use RLS from day one.
- Use simple responsive UI.
- One complete happy path beats five incomplete features.
- App must build successfully before task is considered done.

Deliver:
